<Class name="CM_TCPWorkerController" id="514a19a3-3c8c-4b33-b8a7-c41eea825fda">
    <implementedInterfaces>
        <JadeInterface name="JadeMultiWorkerTcpTransportIF"/>
    </implementedInterfaces>
    <superclass name="CM_InterfaceController"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>CCMS JMTCP01 1024 - Voice Recognition

This class implements the worker application for the TCP listener service.

This class will implement the JadeMultiWorkerTcpTransportIF interface, and provide the 
mechanism to perform the required TCP communication with the client processes.</text>
